      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEAD OF STAFF (7) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Here To Play (24.49) in a T3 RSTW. Took the lead and boxed on but run over. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Good form should continue. ONE LAST TIME (1) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 5 lengths (20.69) at this track. Has the ability to give this a shake. DR. AURORA (2) has mixed form recently, finishing seventh (24.16) in a Bottom Up - Grade 7 at Warragul latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Key player on best and worth another try. TINKER ROCK (8) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
